1
00:01:49,320 --> 00:01:52,120
I'll fight for what I want myself.

2
00:01:52,360 --> 00:01:53,720
I don't need you to go easy on me.

3
00:01:53,720 --> 00:01:55,600
What I want to do is my own freedom.

4
00:01:56,320 --> 00:01:58,050
You have no right to control me.

5
00:01:58,120 --> 00:01:59,320
The match hasn't started yet.

6
00:01:59,320 --> 00:02:00,880
Fine, Xiong Yuanbao.

7
00:02:01,040 --> 00:02:01,970
You've got guts.

8
00:02:02,080 --> 00:02:04,360
You'd better remember what you just said.

9
00:02:04,360 --> 00:02:06,320
Today, I will let you know

10
00:02:06,640 --> 00:02:08,919
what a crushing defeat is.

11
00:02:11,760 --> 00:02:12,620
Xiong Yuanbao.

12
00:02:25,600 --> 00:02:26,600
Xiong Yuanbao, what are you doing?

13
00:02:26,600 --> 00:02:27,920
Why did you throw water at me?

14
00:02:27,920 --> 00:02:29,480
Xiong Yuanbao, what are you doing?

15
00:02:29,480 --> 00:02:30,280
What's wrong?

16
00:02:30,480 --> 00:02:31,400
Xiong Yuanbao,

17
00:02:32,120 --> 00:02:33,440
If you don't want me to enter the competition, just say it.

18
00:02:33,440 --> 00:02:34,960
Why do you treat me like this?

19
00:02:34,960 --> 00:02:36,120
What kind of person are you?

20
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:38,240
You use such despicable tricks when you can't beat us in dancing.

21
00:02:38,240 --> 00:02:39,320
Are you that afraid of us winning?

22
00:02:39,320 --> 00:02:41,160
You throw water because you can't beat us in cheerleading?

23
00:02:41,160 --> 00:02:41,960
What are you talking about?

24
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:43,560
She must have bullied Yuanbao first.

25
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:44,079
How is that possible?

26
00:02:44,079 --> 00:02:44,640
Exactly.

27
00:02:44,680 --> 00:02:46,240
If Gu Xinrui didn't bully her,

28
00:02:46,240 --> 00:02:48,079
why would Yuanbao throw water at you?

29
00:02:48,079 --> 00:02:50,079
She's already like this. How could she verbally abuse anyone?

30
00:02:50,079 --> 00:02:50,680
You guys are too much.

31
00:02:50,680 --> 00:02:51,600
Who bullied you?

32
00:02:51,600 --> 00:02:53,600
You're the one bullying us every time.

33
00:02:53,600 --> 00:02:54,960
You're the one bullying us every time.

34
00:02:54,960 --> 00:02:57,220
We're the ones tolerating it every time.

35
00:03:16,600 --> 00:03:17,600
Are we even?

36
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:19,650
See you on the field.

37
00:04:05,440 --> 00:04:06,960
Wipe yourself with my clothes first.

38
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:09,090
I'll go get a towel from Ruirui for you.

39
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:39,720
Yuanbao,

40
00:04:40,120 --> 00:04:40,840
Yuanbao,

41
00:04:41,080 --> 00:04:41,840
are you okay?

42
00:04:42,520 --> 00:04:43,480
Are you okay?

43
00:04:43,520 --> 00:04:44,800
How did this happen?

44
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:46,960
If I tell you

45
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:49,440
that I didn't splash her,

46
00:04:49,880 --> 00:04:51,480
would you believe me?

47
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:53,400
Of course we believe you.

48
00:04:55,240 --> 00:04:57,080
So she splashed

49
00:04:57,360 --> 00:04:59,080
water on herself.

50
00:05:01,280 --> 00:05:01,960
Qiao Yan.

51
00:05:03,080 --> 00:05:04,000
At that time,

52
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:06,040
no one was there.

53
00:05:07,120 --> 00:05:09,680
They wouldn't believe you even if you told them.

54
00:05:09,680 --> 00:05:11,540
Are we just going to swallow this?

55
00:05:11,920 --> 00:05:14,840
Forget it. Our competition is coming up.

56
00:05:15,960 --> 00:05:17,360
Don't let them affect us.

57
00:05:20,760 --> 00:05:21,360
Okay.

58
00:05:21,760 --> 00:05:22,840
Let's fight them.

59
00:05:23,120 --> 00:05:25,440
Their cheerleading squad is very professional.

60
00:05:25,440 --> 00:05:26,360
You two shouldn't

61
00:05:26,360 --> 00:05:28,420
put too much pressure on yourselves.

62
00:05:28,440 --> 00:05:30,160
We just need to do our best.

63
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:32,820
There's no need to force a comparison with them.

64
00:05:32,920 --> 00:05:34,520
The more she wants us to lose,

65
00:05:34,920 --> 00:05:36,320
the more we can't give up.

66
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:38,210
Let's do our best together.

67
00:05:38,560 --> 00:05:39,120
Let's go.

68
00:05:39,280 --> 00:05:39,880
Let's go.

69
00:05:40,600 --> 00:05:41,440
Let's go.

70
00:05:43,440 --> 00:05:44,640
What happened to your hand?

71
00:05:44,640 --> 00:05:46,300
Why is there such a big bruise?

72
00:05:47,760 --> 00:05:48,560
It's nothing.

73
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:50,600
I accidentally fell yesterday.

74
00:05:50,680 --> 00:05:51,280
It's fine.

75
00:05:51,400 --> 00:05:53,159
It's so purple. It must hurt a lot.

76
00:05:53,159 --> 00:05:54,680
It doesn't hurt. I'm fine.

77
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:56,690
How did this happen?

78
00:05:56,760 --> 00:05:57,920
Did you apply any medicine?

79
00:05:57,920 --> 00:05:59,360
Let me take you to the infirmary.

80
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:00,320
No need.

81
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:02,840
I'm really fine.

82
00:06:03,680 --> 00:06:04,680
Qiao Yan.

83
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:07,920
Is something going on with you?

84
00:06:08,800 --> 00:06:10,600
If you have any difficulties,

85
00:06:11,360 --> 00:06:12,400
just tell us.

86
00:06:12,680 --> 00:06:13,960
We will all help you.

87
00:06:16,520 --> 00:06:17,640
Are you two silly?

88
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:19,250
What could be wrong with me?

89
00:06:19,880 --> 00:06:21,280
Alright, hurry up and go.

90
00:06:21,960 --> 00:06:22,800
Let's go.

91
00:06:22,880 --> 00:06:23,800
So silly.

92
00:06:24,640 --> 00:06:25,480
It's fine.

93
00:06:49,920 --> 00:06:50,720
Shang Ningyu,

94
00:06:51,360 --> 00:06:51,880
should I put it there?

95
00:06:51,880 --> 00:06:53,000
Yes, put it there.

96
00:07:08,640 --> 00:07:11,240
Who do you think will win between the two teams?

97
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:13,770
Do you even have to ask? Definitely Gu Xinrui.

98
00:07:13,920 --> 00:07:15,320
I was on my way here just now

99
00:07:15,320 --> 00:07:16,960
and saw the costumes they changed into.

100
00:07:16,960 --> 00:07:18,220
They are super pretty.

101
00:07:18,680 --> 00:07:19,960
A couple of days ago on the field,

102
00:07:19,960 --> 00:07:21,880
I saw the dance Xiong Yuanbao's team was practicing.

103
00:07:21,880 --> 00:07:23,610
They all looked like gorillas.

104
00:07:23,720 --> 00:07:24,800
It was hilarious.

105
00:07:25,200 --> 00:07:26,440
I saw it too.

106
00:07:26,600 --> 00:07:28,480
The way they looked, oh my god.

107
00:07:29,960 --> 00:07:32,400
Look at Gu Xinrui, she didn't even take the field today,

108
00:07:32,400 --> 00:07:34,730
but she still got her team trained so well.

109
00:07:34,960 --> 00:07:36,400
We'll see the results in a bit.

110
00:07:36,400 --> 00:07:37,320
Come on, students.

111
00:07:37,320 --> 00:07:38,600
Come on, everyone have a seat.

112
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:39,520
Listen up.

113
00:07:39,760 --> 00:07:41,720
The players for our class basketball game

114
00:07:41,720 --> 00:07:43,050
have all been selected.

115
00:07:43,480 --> 00:07:44,880
And the boys have been

116
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:46,600
practicing really well lately.

117
00:07:46,600 --> 00:07:47,400
However,

118
00:07:47,680 --> 00:07:49,040
the girls' cheerleading squad for our class

119
00:07:49,040 --> 00:07:50,440
hasn't been decided yet.

120
00:07:50,600 --> 00:07:51,120
So,

121
00:07:51,200 --> 00:07:52,720
we will use this PE class

122
00:07:52,800 --> 00:07:54,240
to hold a mini-competition.

123
00:07:54,240 --> 00:07:55,680
One team led by Gu Xinrui,

124
00:07:56,159 --> 00:07:57,520
and the other by Xiong Yuanbao.

125
00:07:57,520 --> 00:07:58,760
We will vote

126
00:07:58,840 --> 00:08:00,480
to finally decide which team

127
00:08:00,520 --> 00:08:02,980
will perform at the school basketball game.

128
00:08:03,320 --> 00:08:05,120
Gu Xinrui, get ready to perform.

129
00:08:05,520 --> 00:08:06,480
Okay, Mr. Tian.

130
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:25,330
Look at her outfit and her aura.

131
00:08:25,360 --> 00:08:26,480
Really good.

132
00:08:27,160 --> 00:08:29,680
Just the momentum of a simple entrance wins.

133
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:31,320
Where is Xiong Yuanbao's team?

134
00:08:31,320 --> 00:08:33,049
Why hasn't any of them shown up?

135
00:08:33,240 --> 00:08:34,360
They must be too shabby,

136
00:08:34,360 --> 00:08:35,960
and too embarrassed to come.

137
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:37,120
Maybe they will

138
00:08:37,120 --> 00:08:38,450
just give up in a moment.

139
00:09:38,560 --> 00:09:39,920
Very good. Very good.

140
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:41,480
I didn't expect you

141
00:09:41,560 --> 00:09:43,000
to rehearse this so well in such a short time.

142
00:09:43,000 --> 00:09:44,360
If you perform at the basketball game,

143
00:09:44,360 --> 00:09:46,960
you will definitely be the biggest highlight.

144
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:47,860
Wait, teacher.

145
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:50,360
Yuanbao and the others haven't danced yet.

146
00:09:50,600 --> 00:09:51,480
Right.

147
00:09:52,760 --> 00:09:53,680
Where is Yuanbao?

148
00:09:53,680 --> 00:09:55,120
They are already here, Mr. Tian.

149
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:56,000
I will go find them now.

150
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:56,480
Okay.

151
00:10:10,640 --> 00:10:11,600
Okay, Gu Xinrui.

152
00:10:11,680 --> 00:10:12,940
You guys go take a rest.

153
00:10:17,960 --> 00:10:18,640
How was it?

154
00:10:18,840 --> 00:10:20,370
I told you I was bound to win.

155
00:10:28,720 --> 00:10:29,600
How is it, class monitor?

156
00:10:29,600 --> 00:10:31,000
Are Xiong Yuanbao and her team ready?

157
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:32,400
They are ready, Mr. Tian.

158
00:10:32,520 --> 00:10:33,080
Good.

159
00:10:33,200 --> 00:10:34,400
Come on, get on stage.

160
00:11:43,440 --> 00:11:44,160
Yuanbao!

161
00:11:44,760 --> 00:11:45,640
You can do it!

162
00:12:45,480 --> 00:12:48,400
Everyone only sees her glamorous side,

163
00:12:49,160 --> 00:12:51,890
but they don't know the sweat and tears behind it.

164
00:12:52,840 --> 00:12:54,770
Yuanbao deserves all this praise.

165
00:12:55,680 --> 00:12:58,560
In the future, she will definitely stand on a higher stage

166
00:12:58,560 --> 00:13:00,090
and receive more applause.

167
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:07,480
Mutou.

168
00:13:09,680 --> 00:13:11,940
You think you can buy me with an ice cream?

169
00:13:12,080 --> 00:13:13,040
Of course not.

170
00:13:13,280 --> 00:13:15,640
Don't worry. I'll treat you to a meal this weekend.

171
00:13:15,640 --> 00:13:17,080
Order whatever you want. Eat as much as you can.

172
00:13:17,080 --> 00:13:18,010
Don't hold back.

173
00:13:20,400 --> 00:13:21,160
Mutou,

174
00:13:22,160 --> 00:13:22,960
thank you.

175
00:13:23,520 --> 00:13:24,960
What are you thanking me for this time?

176
00:13:24,960 --> 00:13:25,960
What do you think?

177
00:13:26,160 --> 00:13:28,520
Slowly. Slower.

178
00:13:29,200 --> 00:13:30,800
Come on.

179
00:13:31,440 --> 00:13:32,800
Three, two, one.

180
00:13:33,120 --> 00:13:34,280
Surprise!

181
00:13:37,600 --> 00:13:38,880
Is this...

182
00:13:39,200 --> 00:13:40,130
A friend of mine,

183
00:13:40,240 --> 00:13:42,040
his aunt is a dance teacher here.

184
00:13:42,080 --> 00:13:44,320
She said we can use it for free for a few days.

185
00:13:44,320 --> 00:13:45,200
Really?

186
00:13:45,480 --> 00:13:47,340
Oh my god. Mutou, you're the best.

187
00:13:47,480 --> 00:13:50,040
Now we don't have to train on the playground,

188
00:13:50,440 --> 00:13:52,040
and people won't laugh at us.

189
00:13:52,760 --> 00:13:54,640
Come on. I'll take you to a good place.

190
00:13:54,640 --> 00:13:55,320
Where?

191
00:13:55,480 --> 00:13:56,520
Just follow me.

192
00:13:58,600 --> 00:13:59,560
Two, three, four.

193
00:13:59,560 --> 00:14:00,800
Two, three, four.

194
00:14:01,160 --> 00:14:04,480
Five, six, seven, eight.

195
00:14:04,920 --> 00:14:07,680
Two, two, three, four.

196
00:14:08,360 --> 00:14:10,040
How is it? Any inspiration?

197
00:14:11,120 --> 00:14:12,880
If our performance

198
00:14:13,280 --> 00:14:15,280
also uses this dance style,

199
00:14:15,680 --> 00:14:16,680
what do you think?

200
00:14:16,680 --> 00:14:19,040
Not bad. You're getting the hang of it.

201
00:14:19,440 --> 00:14:20,240
That's it.

202
00:14:20,520 --> 00:14:22,000
Professionally speaking,

203
00:14:22,000 --> 00:14:24,240
we can't beat that Gu Xinrui.

204
00:14:24,280 --> 00:14:26,720
But we can take a different approach.

205
00:14:26,920 --> 00:14:28,650
Surprise is the key to winning.

206
00:14:29,760 --> 00:14:30,400
Exactly.

207
00:14:31,000 --> 00:14:31,560
Right?

208
00:14:34,400 --> 00:14:35,560
Without you,

209
00:14:35,680 --> 00:14:37,600
we wouldn't have won this competition.

210
00:14:37,600 --> 00:14:39,260
Half of the credit goes to you.

211
00:14:40,760 --> 00:14:43,600
Don't be obsessed with me. I'm just a legend.

212
00:14:55,600 --> 00:14:56,840
We can rent this classroom

213
00:14:56,840 --> 00:14:58,440
to you by the hour.

214
00:14:58,520 --> 00:14:59,200
Since you're a student

215
00:14:59,200 --> 00:15:00,880
and have been here so many times,

216
00:15:00,880 --> 00:15:02,680
I'll charge you 20 yuan an hour.

217
00:15:02,760 --> 00:15:03,720
Think about it.

218
00:15:04,000 --> 00:15:05,160
If you want to rent it...

219
00:15:05,160 --> 00:15:06,680
Thank you. I'll rent it.

220
00:15:06,840 --> 00:15:08,000
I'd like to use it today.

221
00:15:08,000 --> 00:15:09,000
Okay, sure.

222
00:15:09,080 --> 00:15:11,280
Then come with me to pay the rent.

223
00:15:19,880 --> 00:15:20,880
Family.

224
00:15:42,520 --> 00:15:43,850
What are you looking at?

225
00:15:45,680 --> 00:15:46,680
Nothing. I'm not looking at anything.

226
00:15:46,680 --> 00:15:49,280
I was just seeing how far you've written.

227
00:16:01,560 --> 00:16:02,820
What's wrong with you?

228
00:16:02,920 --> 00:16:05,050
Why do you keep looking at me like that?

229
00:16:06,600 --> 00:16:08,320
Well, next week, my buddies and I

230
00:16:08,320 --> 00:16:09,920
are going to pull an all-nighter at the internet cafe.

231
00:16:09,920 --> 00:16:12,380
Should I log into your chat app to level it up?

232
00:16:12,880 --> 00:16:13,680
Really?

233
00:16:14,640 --> 00:16:15,440
That's great!

234
00:16:16,200 --> 00:16:18,460
I only have two moons and a star right now.

235
00:16:18,640 --> 00:16:20,520
Brother Qingjun already has three suns.

236
00:16:20,520 --> 00:16:22,160
Even Yuanbao has a sun.

237
00:16:22,360 --> 00:16:23,040
Don't worry.

238
00:16:23,040 --> 00:16:25,120
As long as I go in the future, I'll log in for you.

239
00:16:25,120 --> 00:16:28,040
I promise your level will shoot right up.

240
00:16:29,320 --> 00:16:30,160
Thank you.

241
00:16:32,640 --> 00:16:33,280
Oh, right.

242
00:16:33,520 --> 00:16:35,520
Could you find some time

243
00:16:35,760 --> 00:16:37,890
to decorate my chat app profile for me?

244
00:16:38,040 --> 00:16:40,000
A new skin just came out

245
00:16:40,120 --> 00:16:41,280
called 'Winter Sonata'.

246
00:16:41,280 --> 00:16:42,480
It looks really nice.

247
00:16:44,240 --> 00:16:45,840
My mom is very strict with me.

248
00:16:45,920 --> 00:16:47,650
I can't go to the internet cafe.

249
00:16:49,400 --> 00:16:50,000
Also,

250
00:16:50,480 --> 00:16:51,440
could you check

251
00:16:51,560 --> 00:16:53,400
if anyone visited my profile

252
00:16:54,120 --> 00:16:55,800
or left me any messages?

253
00:16:56,520 --> 00:16:57,240
No problem.

254
00:16:58,360 --> 00:16:59,480
Thanks.

255
00:17:01,760 --> 00:17:02,960
Don't mention it.

256
00:17:03,560 --> 00:17:04,760
We're not strangers.

257
00:17:08,040 --> 00:17:08,720
I mean,

258
00:17:09,240 --> 00:17:10,400
we're good friends,

259
00:17:10,440 --> 00:17:11,839
and good classmates.

260
00:17:13,000 --> 00:17:14,119
It's fine.

261
00:17:15,680 --> 00:17:16,440
Thanks.

262
00:17:16,640 --> 00:17:18,720
No talking. Focus on your homework.

263
00:17:30,120 --> 00:17:31,960
Well? Have you made up your mind?

264
00:17:35,720 --> 00:17:36,640
Class,

265
00:17:37,520 --> 00:17:39,650
after the selection within our class,

266
00:17:40,320 --> 00:17:41,920
congratulations to Xiong Yuanbao's cheerleading squad

267
00:17:41,920 --> 00:17:43,450
for winning by a landslide.

268
00:17:49,360 --> 00:17:50,080
Similarly,

269
00:17:50,680 --> 00:17:51,800
Gu Xinrui's team

270
00:17:51,960 --> 00:17:53,000
was also excellent.

271
00:17:53,000 --> 00:17:54,360
If there's a chance in the future,

272
00:17:54,360 --> 00:17:55,640
we'll take turns.

273
00:17:56,080 --> 00:17:58,280
Let's give them a round of applause too.

274
00:17:59,480 --> 00:18:00,720
I'll say it again.

275
00:18:01,000 --> 00:18:02,520
It's the taking part that counts.

276
00:18:02,520 --> 00:18:05,160
Next up is the autumn sports meet.

277
00:18:05,360 --> 00:18:07,020
And then the basketball game.

278
00:18:07,120 --> 00:18:09,180
I took a look at our class's PE grades.

279
00:18:09,440 --> 00:18:10,640
They are all average.

280
00:18:11,040 --> 00:18:12,200
Although Gong Yu

281
00:18:12,280 --> 00:18:13,410
is a sports student,

282
00:18:13,600 --> 00:18:15,960
he can't participate due to his injury.

283
00:18:16,160 --> 00:18:17,120
So when the time comes,

284
00:18:17,120 --> 00:18:18,160
our class

285
00:18:18,360 --> 00:18:20,120
must give the participating students

286
00:18:20,120 --> 00:18:21,480
the warmest applause.

287
00:18:21,720 --> 00:18:22,920
In terms of momentum,

288
00:18:22,920 --> 00:18:24,160
we definitely can't lose to other classes.

289
00:18:24,160 --> 00:18:24,760
All right?

290
00:18:24,840 --> 00:18:25,600
Yes.

291
00:18:29,640 --> 00:18:31,120
I am a sports student,

292
00:18:31,200 --> 00:18:33,600
but I can't participate in the sports meet.

293
00:18:33,760 --> 00:18:34,640
So funny.

294
00:18:36,040 --> 00:18:38,160
Bro, don't be discouraged.

295
00:18:38,640 --> 00:18:39,770
When you are healed,

296
00:18:39,840 --> 00:18:41,120
there will be chances.

297
00:18:59,160 --> 00:19:00,720
Look who it is.

298
00:19:32,600 --> 00:19:33,680
Come on!

299
00:19:33,760 --> 00:19:35,560
Come on, Gong Yu!

300
00:19:35,720 --> 00:19:37,400
Come on, Gong Yu!

301
00:20:13,520 --> 00:20:14,240
Gong Yu!

302
00:20:14,600 --> 00:20:16,120
Gong Yu's leg is injured,

303
00:20:16,680 --> 00:20:18,810
so he is not qualified to participate.

304
00:20:18,920 --> 00:20:20,520
Even if he stands outside the track,

305
00:20:20,520 --> 00:20:22,380
he still wants to finish the race.

306
00:20:22,640 --> 00:20:23,440
Maybe

307
00:20:23,920 --> 00:20:25,480
this is the real Gong Yu.

308
00:20:26,360 --> 00:20:28,560
We didn't know him well enough before.

309
00:20:36,000 --> 00:20:37,840
Grandma, actually last time,

310
00:20:37,960 --> 00:20:39,640
Gong Yu and I planned

311
00:20:39,680 --> 00:20:41,680
to let you and his grandpa meet

312
00:20:41,720 --> 00:20:42,520
and chat.

313
00:20:43,080 --> 00:20:44,280
But we messed up.

314
00:20:44,720 --> 00:20:47,000
We know you knew each other when you were young.

315
00:20:47,000 --> 00:20:48,000
So,

316
00:20:48,480 --> 00:20:49,800
Grandpa Gong is a really nice person.

317
00:20:49,800 --> 00:20:51,660
Meet him again when you have time.

318
00:20:52,840 --> 00:20:54,040
I am getting old

319
00:20:54,320 --> 00:20:56,120
and don't want to think too much.

320
00:20:56,640 --> 00:20:58,040
All I want now is

321
00:20:58,440 --> 00:21:01,040
for Yuanbao and you to have a good future.

322
00:21:01,680 --> 00:21:03,440
To have a stable job

323
00:21:03,760 --> 00:21:05,480
and a happy family.

324
00:21:06,120 --> 00:21:07,650
That would be enough for me.

325
00:21:08,040 --> 00:21:10,440
Grandma, I know what you're worried about.

326
00:21:11,360 --> 00:21:14,200
Aren't you just worried about what Yuanbao thinks?

327
00:21:14,200 --> 00:21:14,930
Don't worry.

328
00:21:15,240 --> 00:21:16,600
I will talk to her.

329
00:21:17,600 --> 00:21:18,360
Mutou.

330
00:21:21,280 --> 00:21:22,240
Come out with me for a second.

331
00:21:22,240 --> 00:21:23,900
I have something to say to you.

332
00:21:29,120 --> 00:21:30,680
I'll go first, Grandma.

333
00:21:37,200 --> 00:21:38,960
Yuanbao, listen to me.

334
00:21:39,040 --> 00:21:39,760
Say what?

335
00:21:40,040 --> 00:21:42,600
That everything you did is for my own good,

336
00:21:42,800 --> 00:21:44,280
and for Grandma's own good?

337
00:21:44,280 --> 00:21:46,680
Who else would I be doing this for if not you?

338
00:21:46,800 --> 00:21:47,680
Mu Qingyun,

339
00:21:48,320 --> 00:21:50,720
what gives you the right to do this behind my back,

340
00:21:50,720 --> 00:21:53,080
and introduce a partner to my grandma?

341
00:21:55,000 --> 00:21:56,600
Didn't you disagree before?

342
00:21:57,040 --> 00:21:59,120
I thought I'd ask Grandma first.

343
00:21:59,280 --> 00:22:00,920
If she's okay with it,

344
00:22:01,040 --> 00:22:02,360
then I'd discuss it with you.

345
00:22:02,360 --> 00:22:03,160
Mu Qingyun,

346
00:22:03,800 --> 00:22:04,800
can you stay out of

347
00:22:04,880 --> 00:22:06,140
our family's affairs?

348
00:22:07,120 --> 00:22:09,080
Your family's affairs?

349
00:22:11,320 --> 00:22:12,120
That's right.

350
00:22:12,640 --> 00:22:15,240
You'd better stay out of our family's affairs.

351
00:22:18,640 --> 00:22:21,170
Xiong Yuanbao, can you stop being so selfish?

352
00:22:24,840 --> 00:22:25,440
I know you're not ready

353
00:22:25,440 --> 00:22:26,480
for this.

354
00:22:27,600 --> 00:22:29,400
But can you think about Grandma?

355
00:22:29,560 --> 00:22:30,240
Gong Yu's grandfather also

356
00:22:30,240 --> 00:22:31,760
raised him all by himself.

357
00:22:32,200 --> 00:22:33,040
How could he think of

358
00:22:33,040 --> 00:22:35,240
finding a partner for his grandfather?

359
00:22:35,760 --> 00:22:36,360
Yuanbao,

360
00:22:36,840 --> 00:22:38,080
I know you feel bad.

361
00:22:38,880 --> 00:22:40,740
I also know what you're thinking.

362
00:22:41,120 --> 00:22:42,380
You only have Grandma.

363
00:22:42,680 --> 00:22:44,140
You don't want to lose her,

364
00:22:44,200 --> 00:22:46,000
let alone share her with anyone.

365
00:22:55,600 --> 00:22:56,320
But...

366
00:22:57,640 --> 00:23:00,720
It wasn't easy for Grandma to raise you.

367
00:23:01,400 --> 00:23:02,920
Her world can't just revolve around you.

368
00:23:02,920 --> 00:23:03,600
Right?

369
00:23:04,960 --> 00:23:05,820
Think about it.

370
00:23:06,360 --> 00:23:08,160
We're going to college soon.

371
00:23:08,440 --> 00:23:09,960
Are you going to leave her

372
00:23:10,080 --> 00:23:11,120
all alone?

373
00:23:24,880 --> 00:23:26,160
Grandma, I'm not eating.

374
00:23:26,160 --> 00:23:27,240
I'm going to be late.

375
00:23:27,240 --> 00:23:28,400
How can you not eat?

376
00:23:28,480 --> 00:23:29,410
Here, take this.

377
00:23:29,480 --> 00:23:30,440
Eat it at school.

378
00:23:31,160 --> 00:23:31,920
Got it.

379
00:23:38,760 --> 00:23:39,480
Grandma!

380
00:23:44,400 --> 00:23:45,160
Grandma!

381
00:23:45,600 --> 00:23:46,360
Grandma!

382
00:23:47,240 --> 00:23:48,000
Grandma!

383
00:23:49,160 --> 00:23:51,080
Doctor, how is she?

384
00:23:51,960 --> 00:23:53,440
Her blood pressure was just measured.

385
00:23:53,440 --> 00:23:55,640
Systolic 180, diastolic 120.

386
00:23:56,240 --> 00:23:58,640
The dizziness is still caused by high blood pressure.

387
00:23:58,640 --> 00:24:00,040
We'll give her an IV later

388
00:24:00,120 --> 00:24:01,720
to lower her blood pressure.

389
00:24:01,720 --> 00:24:04,040
Ma'am, you can't stop taking your blood pressure medication.

390
00:24:04,040 --> 00:24:05,700
Remember to take it every day.

391
00:24:06,640 --> 00:24:07,720
It's nothing serious.

392
00:24:07,720 --> 00:24:09,480
You don't need so many people to stay here.

393
00:24:09,480 --> 00:24:10,440
One is enough.

394
00:24:11,000 --> 00:24:12,520
Okay, thank you, doctor.

395
00:24:15,240 --> 00:24:16,240
I'm fine.

396
00:24:16,640 --> 00:24:17,720
Don't be afraid.

397
00:24:21,480 --> 00:24:22,960
I'll stay here to take care of Grandma.

398
00:24:22,960 --> 00:24:24,400
You two hurry to school.

399
00:24:25,080 --> 00:24:26,880
I'm not leaving. I want to stay.

400
00:24:27,760 --> 00:24:30,600
Be good. Your studies are important.

401
00:24:31,080 --> 00:24:33,000
Nothing is more important than you.

402
00:24:33,000 --> 00:24:34,560
Say no more. Get some sleep first.

403
00:24:34,560 --> 00:24:35,240
I will stay right here.

404
00:24:35,240 --> 00:24:36,570
I'm not going anywhere.

405
00:24:37,200 --> 00:24:38,480
I'm not going anywhere either.

406
00:24:38,480 --> 00:24:39,760
I will stay and keep you company.

407
00:24:39,760 --> 00:24:41,490
Why are you joining in the fuss?

408
00:24:41,880 --> 00:24:42,940
This is a hospital.

409
00:24:43,000 --> 00:24:44,400
If so many of us stay here,

410
00:24:44,440 --> 00:24:46,000
others won't be able to rest.

411
00:24:46,000 --> 00:24:47,880
Besides, it's not convenient for a boy like you.

412
00:24:47,880 --> 00:24:48,880
Hurry to school.

413
00:24:50,000 --> 00:24:52,160
Mutou, you go to class first.

414
00:24:52,800 --> 00:24:55,240
Don't worry. I'll stay here and keep Grandma company.

415
00:24:55,240 --> 00:24:56,240
Then, Grandma,

416
00:24:57,160 --> 00:24:58,890
I'll come see you after school.

417
00:24:59,280 --> 00:25:00,280
Take care.

418
00:25:00,840 --> 00:25:02,120
Be careful on the road.

419
00:25:02,840 --> 00:25:04,040
Don't worry about me.

420
00:25:05,160 --> 00:25:05,960
Yuanbao,

421
00:25:07,720 --> 00:25:08,720
I'm leaving then.

422
00:25:10,960 --> 00:25:12,020
I'll go see him off.

423
00:25:28,560 --> 00:25:30,160
Nothing is more important than you.

424
00:25:30,160 --> 00:25:31,490
I'll stay here with you.

425
00:25:31,600 --> 00:25:32,730
I won't go anywhere.

426
00:25:38,120 --> 00:25:40,320
Mom, Dad, rest in peace.

427
00:25:40,320 --> 00:25:42,360
I will take good care of Grandma.

428
00:25:59,000 --> 00:26:01,600
What could have happened to Yuanbao's family?

429
00:26:13,320 --> 00:26:14,080
Yuanbao.

430
00:26:15,760 --> 00:26:17,760
You haven't eaten anything all day.

431
00:26:17,840 --> 00:26:19,170
Go get something to eat.

432
00:26:19,240 --> 00:26:20,300
I'll be right here.

433
00:26:20,880 --> 00:26:22,920
I'm not hungry, Auntie.

434
00:26:23,560 --> 00:26:25,600
I'll stay here to take care of Grandma.

435
00:26:25,600 --> 00:26:27,000
You go back and rest.

436
00:26:28,200 --> 00:26:29,720
How can you not eat anything?

437
00:26:29,720 --> 00:26:31,050
Go get something to eat.

438
00:26:31,880 --> 00:26:34,280
School is almost over.

439
00:26:34,800 --> 00:26:36,260
Qingyun will be here soon.

440
00:26:36,360 --> 00:26:38,160
He can also help take care of her.

441
00:26:38,840 --> 00:26:41,770
Then I'll go back to get some toiletries for Grandma.

442
00:26:42,400 --> 00:26:43,400
I'll be back soon.

443
00:26:52,000 --> 00:26:53,260
Be careful on the road.

444
00:27:20,560 --> 00:27:21,480
Who are you?

445
00:27:21,600 --> 00:27:23,330
Have you heard of Brother Shui?

446
00:27:26,760 --> 00:27:27,400
Kid,

447
00:27:28,240 --> 00:27:30,240
leave your name if you have the guts.

448
00:27:42,040 --> 00:27:43,640
What exactly do you want?

449
00:27:57,600 --> 00:27:58,680
How is Grandma?

450
00:28:00,520 --> 00:28:02,320
The doctor came to check a few times.

451
00:28:02,320 --> 00:28:03,980
They said she is quite stable.

452
00:28:05,200 --> 00:28:06,200
Where is Yuanbao?

453
00:28:11,120 --> 00:28:12,440
It's been over an hour.

454
00:28:12,800 --> 00:28:15,880
She said she was going home to get some toiletries for Grandma.

455
00:28:15,880 --> 00:28:17,480
Why hasn't she returned yet?

456
00:28:18,320 --> 00:28:20,840
This child hasn't eaten anything all day.

457
00:28:21,320 --> 00:28:23,120
You'd better go back and check on her.

458
00:28:23,120 --> 00:28:24,880
In case something happens to her on the road,

459
00:28:24,880 --> 00:28:26,410
or she faints or something.

460
00:28:27,920 --> 00:28:28,680
Slow down.

461
00:28:32,680 --> 00:28:33,320
Yuanbao!

462
00:28:34,640 --> 00:28:35,320
Yuanbao!

463
00:28:36,800 --> 00:28:37,440
Yuanbao!

464
00:28:45,480 --> 00:28:46,120
Yuanbao!

465
00:28:57,840 --> 00:28:59,040
She didn't come back.

466
00:29:05,440 --> 00:29:06,000
Ruirui.

467
00:29:11,720 --> 00:29:13,040
Shui.

468
00:29:13,320 --> 00:29:14,560
Didn't we say we'd just scare

469
00:29:14,560 --> 00:29:15,720
and warn her?

470
00:29:16,120 --> 00:29:17,520
If we don't let her go now,

471
00:29:17,560 --> 00:29:18,720
will we get into trouble?

472
00:29:18,720 --> 00:29:19,920
What? Are you scared?

473
00:29:20,480 --> 00:29:23,160
If it were anyone else, a few threats would be enough.

474
00:29:23,160 --> 00:29:25,840
But she happens to be the childhood friend Mu Qingyun cares about.

475
00:29:25,840 --> 00:29:26,520
That punk

476
00:29:26,840 --> 00:29:28,720
made me leave Yuhong in disgrace.

477
00:29:29,520 --> 00:29:30,840
Even now, Niu Ben and his gang

478
00:29:30,840 --> 00:29:32,200
are still laughing at me behind my back.

479
00:29:32,200 --> 00:29:34,520
I was worried I wouldn't get a chance to get revenge.

480
00:29:34,520 --> 00:29:36,720
Finally, such an opportunity has come.

481
00:29:36,840 --> 00:29:37,440
He and I

482
00:29:37,800 --> 00:29:39,000
need to settle this score.

483
00:29:39,000 --> 00:29:41,280
Th-Then what if he calls the police?

484
00:29:41,480 --> 00:29:44,680
What are you panicking for? It's only been a little while.

485
00:29:46,640 --> 00:29:47,440
Little girl,

486
00:29:48,000 --> 00:29:48,800
stop shaking.

487
00:29:49,840 --> 00:29:51,440
Of all the people you could hang out with,

488
00:29:51,440 --> 00:29:53,240
you just had to be Mu Qingyun's sister.

489
00:29:53,240 --> 00:29:54,080
Now look,

490
00:29:54,360 --> 00:29:56,360
you've dragged yourself into this.

491
00:29:56,800 --> 00:29:58,680
You don't need to look at me like that.

492
00:29:58,680 --> 00:30:00,480
I'm just doing a job for someone.

493
00:30:00,520 --> 00:30:01,280
Don't worry,

494
00:30:01,440 --> 00:30:02,960
I'm just giving you a warning.

495
00:30:02,960 --> 00:30:04,080
As long as you behave,

496
00:30:04,080 --> 00:30:05,360
I won't make things hard for you.

497
00:30:05,360 --> 00:30:06,320
But now,

498
00:30:07,680 --> 00:30:09,810
you need to call Mu Qingyun here for me.

499
00:30:14,760 --> 00:30:15,720
Is Yuanbao with you?

500
00:30:15,720 --> 00:30:16,640
Yuanbao?

501
00:30:17,320 --> 00:30:18,840
Didn't you say you had a family emergency

502
00:30:18,840 --> 00:30:19,880
and took the day off today?

503
00:30:19,880 --> 00:30:20,760
Okay, got it.

504
00:30:21,520 --> 00:30:22,200
Yuanbao.

505
00:30:27,840 --> 00:30:28,970
Is Yuanbao with you?

506
00:30:29,480 --> 00:30:30,740
She didn't contact me.

507
00:30:31,680 --> 00:30:33,080
I haven't seen her today.

508
00:30:33,200 --> 00:30:35,260
What's wrong? Did something happen?

509
00:30:36,600 --> 00:30:37,730
Where have you been?

510
00:30:42,120 --> 00:30:42,720
Xinrui.

511
00:30:42,840 --> 00:30:45,320
Come, taste how the chicken soup is.

512
00:30:48,400 --> 00:30:49,120
Xinrui.

513
00:30:50,040 --> 00:30:51,320
Come, have a taste.

514
00:30:51,520 --> 00:30:52,080
Okay.

515
00:30:53,160 --> 00:30:54,080
Did you get burned?

516
00:30:54,080 --> 00:30:54,480
It's fine.

517
00:30:54,480 --> 00:30:54,920
Did you get burned?

518
00:30:54,920 --> 00:30:55,450
I'm fine.

519
00:30:55,560 --> 00:30:57,240
Jingu, what are you spacing out for?

520
00:30:57,240 --> 00:30:58,570
Hurry up and get a towel.

521
00:30:59,320 --> 00:31:00,050
Are you okay?

522
00:31:00,360 --> 00:31:01,800
It's fine, Auntie.

523
00:31:02,680 --> 00:31:03,400
Xinrui,

524
00:31:04,360 --> 00:31:06,640
has something been on your mind recently?

525
00:31:06,640 --> 00:31:07,770
Did Jingu bully you?

526
00:31:08,280 --> 00:31:09,040
No, no.

527
00:31:09,160 --> 00:31:12,680
Uncle, I'm just feeling a bit stressed with my studies.

528
00:31:13,160 --> 00:31:16,020
After all, I've fallen too far behind in my classes.

529
00:31:16,480 --> 00:31:17,760
Your health is important.

530
00:31:17,760 --> 00:31:19,420
Don't just focus on studying.

531
00:31:19,480 --> 00:31:22,080
Have Jingu take you out for a walk this weekend.

532
00:31:22,240 --> 00:31:24,240
Don't always stay cooped up at home.

533
00:31:25,000 --> 00:31:26,400
Got it. Thank you, Uncle.

534
00:31:27,400 --> 00:31:29,320
I'm full. I'm going to study.

535
00:31:55,200 --> 00:31:56,960
Xiong Yuanbao, where are you?

536
00:31:57,080 --> 00:31:59,610
Aren't you too old to pull a disappearing act?

537
00:32:02,120 --> 00:32:03,000
Where is she?
